            "button_2_url": "#",
            "set_menu_bottom_text": "<p>Set Menus are required for groups larger than 12 people at both lunch and dinner and are perfect for your Christmas work function, family celebration, business dinner or social group event.</p>\n       <p>Menus are taken from the a la carte menus of the season, so they are current & subject to seasonal changes. A silent option is available on request for vegetarian & vegan diners as required. Special dietary requirements can be catered for by arrangement.</p>\n       <p><strong>Please note: Set Menus are only available by prior arrangement, and bookings are essential.</strong></p>",
