            "tab_title": "Locals Lunch",
            "image_first": "shopify://shop_images/The-Mission-Estate-Rose-all-Day-FAWC-Summer-2019-20_1.png",
            "set_menu_heading": "$58.00 Bites + 2 Courses",
            "set_menu_price": "$70.00 Bites + 3 Courses",
            "set_menu_text": "<div class=\"wrap_local_lunch\">\n  <p>Embrace the seasons with our Locals Lunch menu. A celebration of seasonal change and the region’s finest ingredients. Savour a thought fully crafted 2 or 3 course menu with small bitesto start, complemented by esteemed Mission Estate wines.</p>\n  <p>Book Now to reserve a table to Lunch like a local</p> \n   <div class=\"note_wraps\">\n      <p>*Available Monday - Friday 11.30am - 2.30pm</p>\n      <p>*Menu is subject to change based on the availability of seasonal ingredients</p>\n      <p>*All guests must dine off the same menu unless arranged prior</p>\n    </div>  \n</div>",
            "image_second": "shopify://shop_images/113755-Mission-Estate_1.png",
